Package: barista
Type: Package
Title: Tools for the Analysis and Visualisation of Lineage Tracing Barcodes
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Dane", "Vassilaidis", email = "dane.vassiliadis@petermac.org",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Dane Vassiliadis <dane.vassiliadis@petermac.org>
Description: A toolkit for the analysis and visualisation of lineage tracing
    experiments using DNA barcodes. Additionally, a series of functions to link DNA barcoding 
    results with scRNA-seq/scATAC-seq datasets is provided. 
